div.p: REUTLINGEN, a handſome, free, and imperial town oſ Germany, in the circle oſ Suabia, and duchy of wirtemberg ; ſeated in a plain on the river Eſchez, near the Neckar, adorned with handſome public buildings, and has a well frequented college. E. Long. 9. 10. N. Lat. 48. 31.
